sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant UserDomain as User (Domain)
    participant SessionService
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events
    participant Notif as UserNotifications

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/users/{userId}/suspend
    Note right of Client: {reason: "Spam submissions"}

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract userId and reason
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create SuspendUserCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(SuspendUserCommand)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check reason is provided
    Validator->>Validator: Verify admin role
    Validator->>DB: Check user exists
    DB-->>Validator: User found ✓
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get user entity
    DB-->>Handler: User

    Handler->>UserDomain: user.Suspend(reason)
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Set IsSuspended = true
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Set SuspendedAt = UtcNow
    UserDomain->>UserDomain: Set SuspensionReason
    UserDomain->>Events: Raise UserSuspendedEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(user)
    DB-->>Handler: User updated ✓

    Handler->>SessionService: InvalidateAllUserSessions(userId)
    SessionService->>DB: Mark all sessions as revoked
    DB-->>SessionService: Sessions invalidated ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish UserSuspendedEvent
    Events->>Notif: Send suspension notification

    Handler-->>Mediator: Success
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: Success

    Endpoint-->>Client: 204 No Content

    Note over Notif: Email sent to user
    Notif->>Notif: Create notification
    Notif->>Notif: Send email alert
